    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Synthetically prepared red iron oxide pigment. It is a permanent pigment, having good tinting strength and good oil-drying properties, and ranging in color from scarlet to maroon. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
